Welcome to OpenAstro PHD2 Version @VERSION@

This is the OpenAstro fork of PHD2, supporting ASCOM Alpaca and INDI
equipment drivers only. It is free, open source, and intended for use
with AlpacaBridge and INDI server workflows.

PHD2's built-in help file is an excellent way to get started using the
program, regardless of whether you've had previous experience with the
original PHD.

For project information, releases, and bug reports, visit

   https://github.com/open-astro/phd2-alpaca-indi
   https://openastro.net/

This fork is based on PHD2 by openphdguiding.org. For questions about
the original upstream PHD2, see

   https://openphdguiding.org/
   https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/open-phd-guiding

The OpenAstro Team
